{"id":823,"date":"2009-04-30T21:35:48","date_gmt":"2009-05-01T02:35:48","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/the_writers_type.php"},"modified":"2009-04-30T21:35:48","modified_gmt":"2009-05-01T02:35:48","slug":"the_writers_type","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/the_writers_type.php","title":{"rendered":"The Writer&apos;s Type"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/little_brown_logo.gif\" alt=\"Little, Brown and Company Logo, Before and After\" \/><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/www.littlebrown.co.uk\/About\/Imprints\/LittleBrown\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Little, Brown and Company<\/a> was founded in 1837, publishing fiction and nonfiction titles from great American writers including great names such as Norman Mailer, Gore Vidal and E. L. Doctorow, and brilliant satirists like David Sedaris and Candace Bushnell. They are a publishing group under <a href=\"http:\/\/www.hachettebookgroup.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Hachette Book Group<\/a> who is a subsidiary of <a href=\"http:\/\/www.lagardere.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Lagard\u001are<\/a>, a communications and media company. The previous identity was primarily an illustration of the <a href=\"http:\/\/www.mass.gov\/?pageID=mg2terminal&#038;L=5&#038;L0=Home&#038;L1=State+Government&#038;L2=About+Massachusetts&#038;L3=Interactive+State+House&#038;L4=Inside+the+State+House&#038;sid=massgov2&#038;b=terminalcontent&#038;f=interactive_statehouse_bulfinch&#038;csid=massgov2 <http:\/\/www.mass.gov\/?pageID=mg2terminal&amp;L=5&amp;L0=Home&amp;L1=State+Government&amp;L2=About+Massachusetts&amp;L3=Interactive+State+House&amp;L4=Inside+the+State+House&amp;sid=massgov2&amp;b=terminalcontent&amp;f=interactive_statehouse_bulfinch&amp;cs> &#8221; target=&#8221;_blank&#8221;>Bulfinch Monument<\/a> &mdash;\u001aa not-so-well-known Boston landmark. Hard to reproduce and a bit far from conveying literary notions for those unfamiliar with Little, Brown&#8217;s history. The new identity, created by <a href=\"http:\/\/www.lancehidy.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Lance Hidy<\/a>, employs <a href=\"http:\/\/new.myfonts.com\/fonts\/agfa\/silica\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Silica<\/a> to craft a couple of typewriter keys, forming a monogram-like mark. Simple, reproducible, and memorable enough to work well on a book spine or in trade ads. Paired with a cleanly set nameplate when needed &mdash; this is a successful rebranding. You can read a bit more on the redesign and hear from Hidy over at <a href=\"http:\/\/www.observer.com\/2009\/media\/little-brown-ditches-bulfinch-monument-debuts-new-logo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The New York Observer<\/a>.<\/p>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/images\/excerpt_empty.gif\" alt=\"Excerpt Empty\" \/>","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"episode_type":"","audio_file":"","duration":"","filesize":"","date_recorded":"","explicit":"","block":"","filesize_raw":""},"categories":[9,63,26],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/823"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/4"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=823"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/823\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=823"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=823"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=823"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}